data.description:
Discover the epitome of lake living in this updated 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath gem nestled in scenic Texas Township. Embrace the tranquility just steps from Eagle Lake, with private access to a sandy beach and shaded park area fully equipped with picnic tables, benches, and a play structure! As a bonus, the association offers a private shared dock, and you have the option to secure your own slip by joining the waiting list. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style with the cozy main floor living room with stone fireplace or make your way upstairs to the spacious 2nd living space, ideal for both relaxation & entertaining. The updated kitchen with granite counter tops is the perfect place to gather with family or friends over yummy delights. Savor quiet mornings within the enclosed sunroom with views of the expansive backyard. The extra large shed is the perfect place to hold all of your lake toys and lawn equipment. Don't miss the opportunity to call this lake haven your new home. 

Upgrades within the last 2.5 years include-
New roof, new natural gas forced air furnace, new mini split heating and cooling system for the 2nd floor, new in-line water filter, fully updated kitchen with new granite countertops, cabinets, kitchen plumbing fixtures, lights fixtures, and trim. All new paint throughout the home and garage. New pantry in the laundry area. New carpet on the stairs and in the master bedroom.
